\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2.1}{\ignorespaces A basic echo state network architecture. $W^{out}$ edges are trainable. $W^{in}$ and $W^{res}$ are fixed after the network architecture is created and are not updated during training.\blx@tocontentsinit {0}\parencite {9093897}}}{5}{figure.2.1}%
